Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

The world of Marvel's superheroes clash with the fighters from Capcom in one of the finest 2D fighters too hit the DreamCast.

Using your team beat all comers into submission with your combos and team-up attacks and become the greatest team in fighting history. Theres cameos for characters from both universes, who pop in to help the fight, as your random "helper" characters

All the usual modes are included the standard arcade, versus, survival, and training modes as well as the cross-fever mode that allows 2 Vs 2 fighting mode with 4 pads.